  "detailed_description": "After waking up in a mysterious place, you quickly discover three things: <br><br>-Everyone there has supernatural abilities.<br>-It’s not a safe place.<br>-And your hosts are either aliens, monsters from another dimension, or seriously messed up human beings.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/da6fe5bdd317f587b0c8a7b5a8c4b26d.poster.avif?t=1772897193\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/da6fe5bdd317f587b0c8a7b5a8c4b26d.webm?t=1772897193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/da6fe5bdd317f587b0c8a7b5a8c4b26d.mp4?t=1772897193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve nearly 70 easy-to-understand but difficult-to-solve puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/56cd82a88ba3e8105f4e8c911a33dcfc.poster.avif?t=1772897193\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/56cd82a88ba3e8105f4e8c911a33dcfc.webm?t=1772897193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/56cd82a88ba3e8105f4e8c911a33dcfc.mp4?t=1772897193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Uncover the mysteries of this strange, uncertain place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740410/extras/7d06e99956ede9959caf2e2933a7f36b.poster.avif?t=1772897193\" width=800 height=218 ><sou